[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Understanding XMLCatalog choices**\n\nI need to figure out how the XMLCatalog selects an external resolver. There seems to be some nuance in the decision-making process that I want to grasp. I'm curious about the conditions that lead to different choices for resolution. I wonder if certain parameters or configurations weigh into that selection. It definitely feels like exploring a deeper layer of functionality within the XMLCatalog. Let's see what I can discover about that process!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0de4b39fe136b6300169fb93c74130819e8543a48d12fb93ef\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-5PLevdPMFVpkVAJ_WKPvnLAxEGyWnLS4o5KQ4jHZIjrTybc7XuBM9XiBbc2s8rRRoXZ8Vukajzfj4Gsoc89OfaU1lmIXZVKuyPlcWH7Y0gaqOdXoFc_qLNtfUY3fE5chnS9DGMiB7KcZJspNTkuAhNkWGCHdeP911EboXEY4JALtkYfEK9r3wetqIiabrUZ9u3Vd60L1FcLZWWbsfNsPJfdGYW5DiV0YoLwuXPHnIlLeK3TDEgWcIabeXVXgdIOMKduXq_waaW2wXrznA0RBV3cPqDLHHouVxn2Sqy0b8kQKL1pJpAsMHc5EaasWV7HJlQMGdDo_wCjsqhPLZ2Co-Joa47_Sv-CgIuFkxD8ID_baSZXzA1AWIxjecF5cgPcpSw8U_x77ibmjeLjPentJgz-AfL9fV66_t3nqkbZvYKU8xBJKWd9UeedwCyhWIJenYZzENJPjQuDtHOIRSpgt7rYh3EhREsZoq1e85qyCP1Ikng6dd7h8LdPEcYPA6M3uKJ4wcqHEOfqUODeqlE9ZYTEm_nAWDTXUr8sOoneAONXABEh4qosF19Tfe7bAR-iPbRpWIH2CLpPVs2VuNBqzqihzowuN1LNEGLWi81FdgETxZxQ5r5xGT7O0yZKyA9kOMnUFvO-3cod2xthOQ7vbwkzefJ6RR35nlqWPmG4RoLNBb6duBDVha52QHYFW2xWGggg4fJaKWcMyv-Tu73rv5ZU1aJRdCu99nYuzjGGvKidUxxVxKFFIHxq1FXfzxPKUbnR7IF1pkQRRJvdbPALvQhNPphZC8Ht3ToB494J-NrFLS-1khE1QOMJ4yPNFi36F_JaAj2OxjEE5O-Dm3jF0NtLpMYU9B8SIxABk_ypEA70yFpPG7ZCThmdOrPGUiQRMBQQ6spUsC8DTUhVcB8_kb4AVX3V2WVifMAJ1pBFnLapwf8q_Dk2d3MDAi2MtgcZwZTB4w-1K5vXXJX54wrar1BPklfT_xyh9PKVVYl954oy3daoTOrywok5v5GSH6mP8Tag\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Understanding XMLCatalog choices**\\n\\nI need to figure out how the XMLCatalog selects an external resolver. There seems to be some nuance in the decision-making process that